snippet.title: Endless Nightmare: Weird Hospital
snippet.description:
Endless Nightmare: Weird Hospital is the prequel to Endless Nightmare, the protagonist is still James! Let’s take a look at the story that happened before James’ scary house! James wakes up in the scary hospital, he is investigating the case that the people are missing in the Oak Town, dangers are everywhere in the weird hospital. What kind of weird and bizarre case will he encounter? What amazing secret is hidden in the weird hospital? 
It seems that he has a close connection with the case! This time, James will take weapons to a contest between justice and evil!
